{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% block body %}
	<div class="jumbotron">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Welcome to Watch'n'Sing!</h1>
    		<p>Have you ever tried to watch a video on YouTube and sing at the same time with having lyrics on a separate tab in your browser? If you did, then you, probably, thought that it is not really convenient. You are at the right site right now - get the video and the lyrics on the same page!</p>
    		<form method="GET" action="/search">
        <div>
          <input class="search artist" type="search" id="artist" name="artist" placeholder="Enter Artist">
